<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.8">
<l>akaṟṟa nīvaitta māyaval laimpulaṅkaḷā mavai naṉkaṟintaṉaṉ</l>
<l>akaṟṟi yeṉṉaiyu nīyaruñ cēṟṟil vīḻtti kaṇṭāy</l>
<l>pakaṟkatir maṇimāṭa nīṭu cirīvara maṅkai vāṇaṉē yeṉṟum</l>
<l>pukaṟkariya ventāy puḷḷiṉvāy piḷantāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Well I knew those that are the five senses strong in illusion which you put so that they forsake [me],</l>
<l>and after having forsaken [me] you let me fall into the difficult [to escape] mud, see,</l>
<l>o resident of Cirīvaramaṅkai tall with storied mansion with rayed gems by day,</l>
<l>may father who is difficult to enter, he who tore the mouth of the bird.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
